## Summary
This document is Part 1 of the Data Taxonomy Playbook, introducing the importance of well-planned instrumentation for event-based analytics platforms. It covers defining business goals, understanding user journeys, identifying critical paths, and establishing data governance rules before implementing an event taxonomy in Amplitude.

